Besepa Gateway for WooCommerce and WooCommerce Subscriptions.

== Description ==

Using the Besepa Gateway, your customers can make payments directly from their bank accounts instead using a credit card.

== Installation ==

1. Upload the plugin files to the `/wp-content/plugins/woocommerce-besepa` directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' screen in WordPress
3. Use the WooCommerce->Settings screen to configure the besepa gateway

